                            <p class="time sm-text">your reviews :</p><br>
                            <h6>A masterpiece!</h6>
                            <!-- <p class="time sm">01 February 2017</p> -->
                            <p>“To put it simply, the movie is fascinating, exciting and fantastic. The dialog, the fight choreography, the way the story moves, the characters charisma, all and much more are combined together to deliver this masterpiece.
                                Such an amazing flow, providing a fusion between the 90s and the new century, it's like the assassins are living in another world, with another mindset, without people understanding it. Just one advice for you though: Don't
